Really? What did he say?

53
00:07:31,308 --> 00:07:31,796
喂！
Hello!

54
00:07:31,941 --> 00:07:32,907
喂，表妹呀？
Hello, little cousin!

55
00:07:33,176 --> 00:07:34,302
华哥起床了没有？
Haven't Brother Wah get up?

56
00:07:35,412 --> 00:07:36,207
喂！
Hello!

57
00:07:36,313 --> 00:07:37,939
我现在还在肥九那儿收数
I'm still staying with Fat-karl for collecting debt

58
00:07:38,248 --> 00:07:40,875
有没搞错，今早收到现在还没收到
Damn it! You still haven't get the money till now?

59
00:07:41,184 --> 00:07:43,516
明明是玩你，你不要走开，我马上来
He's just making fun of you! You stay there and I come at once!

60
00:07:56,599 --> 00:07:57,998
我今晚没空陪你吃饭
I cannot go for dinner

61
00:07:58,135 --> 00:07:59,193
你自己出去吃吧
with you tonight!

62
00:08:02,905 --> 00:08:04,532
这里有一百元，你拿去吃饭
Here's one hundred dollars for your dinner!

63
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:05,966
钥匙在地毯底下
