64
00:08:08,211 --> 00:08:10,041
除了它吧，很好看吗？！
Take it off, would you? It isn't looking good

65
00:08:22,159 --> 00:08:23,592
先喝杯茶吧！
Have a cup of tea first!

66
00:08:28,098 --> 00:08:30,464
肥九，我跟你讲
Fat-karl, I tell you...

67
00:08:31,001 --> 00:08:32,661
我乌蝇肯跟你讲这么久
I'm doing you favour to talk with you

68
00:08:32,868 --> 00:08:34,165
算是给足面子你了
for such a long time

69
00:08:35,871 --> 00:08:37,236
我乌蝇的名字不够响
I, Fly, am not famous

70
00:08:37,441 --> 00:08:38,907
不是我不够QuaIi
because I'm not qualified

71
00:08:39,276 --> 00:08:41,766
是我大佬教我做人要深藏不露
also my Big Brother always tell me to be subtle

72
00:08:42,245 --> 00:08:43,836
牛池湾飞机你认识吧？！
Did you know Mr Aeroplane of Agah-chee Wan?!

73
00:08:44,014 --> 00:08:45,810
他在我们场里签了一千六百元的单
He had made a debt of $1600

74
00:08:45,981 --> 00:08:47,209
不过是拖了两天
and just paid it late for two days,

75
00:08:47,384 --> 00:08:49,579
现在飞不起啦，还要坐轮椅呢！
now he cannot fly, and have to sit on a wheel chair

76
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:53,046
这件事还是我乌蝇亲手做的
I did that with my own hands

77
00:08:54,623 --> 00:08:55,954
你这是抛我啦？！
Are you trying to frighten me?

78
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:59,253
飞机他算是老几呀？拿他来跟我比
He, Aeroplane, is a nobody and cannot be compared to me

79
00:08:59,496 --> 00:09:00,689
我告诉你呀
I tell you...

80
00:09:00,930 --> 00:09:01,896
我肥九出来混
I, Fat-karl,

81
00:09:02,065 --> 00:09:03,759
向来没有找数这个习惯
never before have the habit of paying debt

82
00:09:03,966 --> 00:09:07,458
别说是你，大圈那个向东够恶了吧？
Let's say that Big-Circle who were more powerful...

83
00:09:07,636 --> 00:09:08,967
现在也变成细圈啦！
and now Big-Circle becomes Small-Circle!

84
00:09:09,172 --> 00:09:10,832
你知道是为了什么？
Do you know why?

85
00:09:11,007 --> 00:09:12,906
就是因为他拿叠单来叫我找数
It was because he forced me to pay his debt,

86
00:09:13,009 --> 00:09:14,442
被我打得他五官不全
so I hit him nearly into death

87
00:09:14,610 --> 00:09:16,407
现在只剩下一只眼啦！
He now get only one eye left!

88
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:18,940
出来混了才不过两年
Just having two years experience

89
00:09:19,149 --> 00:09:20,979
够胆来向我肥九收数？
don't you have the guts to collect my debt?

90
00:09:21,251 --> 00:09:24,913
我肥九的刀疤多过你的脚毛呀！
I got knife-scars more than the number of your leg's hair!

91
00:09:25,322 --> 00:09:28,416
刀疤？我大哥得一条，你有，我切！
Scar? My Big Brother has one! I'll cut myself if you have!

92
00:09:29,092 --> 00:09:30,615
你切啦！
Cut yourself then!

93
00:09:32,262 --> 00:09:33,250
还没讲完？！
Haven't you finish talking?

94
00:09:33,597 --> 00:09:35,257
还在讲开场白
We're in the beginning still!

95
00:09:35,965 --> 00:09:37,829
讲了几个钟头，还只是讲开场白？
Still in the beginning for so many hours!

96
00:09:38,268 --> 00:09:39,097
你找死呀？！
Don't you want to die?

97
00:09:39,236 --> 00:09:41,135
别动，统统不要动！
Don't move! Everybody don't move!

98
00:09:41,304 --> 00:09:43,794
给不给钱？给不给？！
Would you pay the debt?

99
00:09:44,474 --> 00:09:47,806
给，给，我没说不给！
Yes, yes! Why wouldn't I?

100
00:09:50,313 --> 00:09:52,406
想不到会这么顺利的
It's unbelievable! So easy!

101
00:09:52,982 --> 00:09:54,972
看他的样就知道是鳄鱼头，老衬底啦
I know, just by his face, that he is a sheep wearing tiger's skin

102
00:09:55,218 --> 00:09:56,013
有这么多人在
With so many companions,

103
00:09:56,186 --> 00:09:57,777
要有本事的话，早就动你了
they will strike you in the very beginning if they have guts

104
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:58,647
你说得对！
You are right!

105
00:09:58,754 --> 00:09:59,413
这个给你！
This is for you!

106
00:09:59,556 --> 00:10:00,419
谢谢大佬！
Thank you, Brother!

107
00:10:04,427 --> 00:10:05,085
大佬，你到那里去？
Where are you going Big Brother?

108
00:10:12,402 --> 00:10:13,231
华哥！
Brother Wah!

109
00:10:15,572 --> 00:10:16,333
你来找Mabel？
Visiting Mabel?

110
00:10:16,473 --> 00:10:16,801
是呀！
Yeah!

111
00:10:16,972 --> 00:10:17,960
她还没上班呢！
She hasn't go for work yet!

112
00:10:18,441 --> 00:10:19,202
我到下面去等她
I'll wait for her downstairs

113
00:10:19,276 --> 00:10:19,969
好呀！
OK!

114
00:10:35,325 --> 00:10:36,951
那间Boutique有好多新货到了
That boutique has a lot of new arrival!

115
00:10:37,127 --> 00:10:37,717
是吗？
Really?

116
00:10:37,893 --> 00:10:38,587
改天跟你一起去看吧！
I'll go to the boutique with you some other day!

117
00:10:38,727 --> 00:10:39,591
好呀！
OK!

118
00:10:45,402 --> 00:10:48,234
Mabel!
Mabel!

119
00:10:48,704 --> 00:10:49,728
来！
Come here!

120
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:54,070
我还没吃饭，一齐去宵夜吧！
I didn't have my dinner! Would you go eating with me!

121
00:10:58,114 --> 00:10:59,637
不喜欢就算了
That's OK if you don't like to!

122
00:11:02,818 --> 00:11:05,718
为什么这么晚才返工？
Why did you go to work so lately?

123
00:11:05,888 --> 00:11:06,854
我刚刚才出院
I just left from the hospital

124
00:11:07,957 --> 00:11:11,290
刚刚出院？！又去洗胃？！
Just from the hospital? Why? Stomach-washing again?

125
00:11:11,428 --> 00:11:12,894
不是洗胃，是堕胎呀！
Not stomach-washing! It's abortion!

126
00:11:18,601 --> 00:11:19,693
讲笑是吗？
Are you kidding?

127
00:11:19,835 --> 00:11:21,200
你可以当我讲笑
You can treat it as kidding if you like to!

128
00:11:25,208 --> 00:11:27,675
不是吧，有了也不告诉我？
No it won't! Why didn't you tell me that you were pregnant?

129
00:11:28,211 --> 00:11:29,542
你有给机会我跟你讲吗？
Had you gave me a chance to tell me?

130
00:11:29,745 --> 00:11:31,838
我等了你三天，你有没CaII过我？
I had waited for three day! But didn't you call me?

131
00:11:32,982 --> 00:11:35,814
