134
00:11:40,490 --> 00:11:41,456
还是叫你跟我结婚？
or tell you to marry me?

135
00:11:41,591 --> 00:11:44,081
认识了你六年，我得到些什么？
We'd been together for six years! What did I get finally?

136
00:11:44,394 --> 00:11:46,487
人，我有等于没有
I felt like not knowing you

137
00:11:46,629 --> 00:11:48,221
钱，就更加不用说了
and didn't even get any money

138
00:11:48,465 --> 00:11:51,559
我霉得连堕胎的钱都要向老妈借呢！
I'm so poor that I had to borrow my mother's money for abortion!

139
00:11:51,700 --> 00:11:52,666
