Speak up! What did I do for?

140
00:11:52,901 --> 00:11:54,129
住口！
Shut up!

141
00:11:57,740 --> 00:11:58,297
你从认识我那天开始
Stop saying! Since the day we'd met,

142
00:11:58,575 --> 00:11:59,734
就知道我是个什么人
you knew already what kind of person I am

143
00:12:02,078 --> 00:12:05,514
你想结婚，想赚钱就不要跟着我
Don't stay with me if you want to marry & want money

144
00:12:06,915 --> 00:12:08,507
你别以为一声不响的去堕了胎
Don't think that because you had abortion so secretly

145
00:12:08,717 --> 00:12:09,911
