so that you'll feel guilty for the rest of your life

153
00:12:30,373 --> 00:12:33,205
你行，算你行！
You've got the guts!

154
00:13:13,949 --> 00:13:14,846
表哥！
Cousin!

155
00:13:18,088 --> 00:13:19,112
你没事吧？
Are you alright?

156
00:13:44,314 --> 00:13:45,177
表哥！
Cousin!

157
00:13:48,385 --> 00:13:52,081
表哥，有什么事吗？
What's the matter, cousin?

158
00:13:53,490 --> 00:13:54,922
