Or else, I'll throw you out!

163
00:15:37,893 --> 00:15:38,951
你不用去看医生？
Did you see the doctor?

164
00:15:39,928 --> 00:15:41,293
刚刚看完回来
I just returned from the hospital

165
00:15:43,599 --> 00:15:44,725
医生怎么说？
What have the doctor said?

166
00:15:45,701 --> 00:15:47,032
明天才有报告
I will get the report tomorrow!

167
00:15:57,580 --> 00:16:00,377
吃过饭没有？我跟你出去吃吧！
Haven't you have your meal? Go eating with me!

168
00:16:01,884 --> 00:16:03,078
我煮了饭啦！
I have make the meal!

169
00:16:14,063 --> 00:16:15,757
今早乌蝇又打过电话来
Fly had phoned you again this morning

170
00:16:18,067 --> 00:16:19,193
那衰仔有什么话讲呀？
What had the dirty guy said?

171
00:16:20,570 --> 00:16:23,504
没什么，只聊了两句
Nothing special! Just some casual talk!

172
00:16:25,008 --> 00:16:26,373
有没有问我的事呀？
Didn't he ask anything about me?

173
00:16:26,975 --> 00:16:27,770
你什么事？
What kind of thing?

174
00:16:30,679 --> 00:16:32,203
昨晚的事呀
The thing happened last night!

175
00:16:36,952 --> 00:16:38,510
