Fly had asked only once!

176
00:16:40,622 --> 00:16:43,955
问一句？问些什么？
What? What did he ask?

177
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:46,393
我不敢讲！
I'm afraid to tell you!

178
00:16:48,431 --> 00:16:49,988
有什么话你讲好了
Just tell me what you heard!

179
00:16:50,832 --> 00:16:52,163
真的讲呀？！
Do you insist me to tell you?

180
00:16:54,504 --> 00:16:56,027
