00:45:50,238 --> 00:45:51,296
文又不行，武也不行
You can't do anything

551
00:45:51,439 --> 00:45:52,735
整天紧着出来行
Just hang around

552
00:45:53,041 --> 00:45:54,599
说了你不是这种材料啦
You are not anything

553
00:45:54,741 --> 00:45:56,504
是，我不是这种材料
Yeah, I'm not anything

554
00:45:56,677 --> 00:45:58,008
我最适合去卖鱼旦
I can only sell fishballs

555
00:45:59,280 --> 00:46:01,179
好，你叫我卖我便去卖罗
You ask me to do that

556
00:46:01,882 --> 00:46:03,008
卖到有一天我受不了
If I can't stand anymore

557
00:46:03,184 --> 00:46:05,083
我放些山埃落去毒死他们吧
I'll put poison on the fishballs

558
00:46:08,955 --> 00:46:10,354
为你好吧，你知不知呀？
It's good for you. Do you understand?

559
00:46:28,309 --> 00:46:32,473
Hi，这么巧呀？
Hi, what a coincident!

560
00:46:32,713 --> 00:46:34,146
对呀，真巧！
Right! Really a coincident!

561
00:46:37,784 --> 00:46:38,750
你好吗？
How are you?

562
00:46:39,920 --> 00:46:48,259
好！…我结婚了
Fine! I have married!

563
00:46:55,570 --> 00:46:59,562
好事，你老公对你怎么样？
Good! Are your husband treating you good?

564
00:47:00,441 --> 00:47:01,600
不错！
Quite good!

565
00:47:07,181 --> 00:47:09,342
这么大的雨，也不知要等到什么时候
So heavy is the rain! Who knows hot long will I have to wait!

566
00:47:10,184 --> 00:47:12,151
我在等我老公来接我
I'm waiting for my husband!

567
00:47:15,223 --> 00:47:16,485
抽不抽烟呀？
Have a cigarette?

568
00:47:16,957 --> 00:47:18,219
我戒了！
I didn't smoke anymore!

569
00:47:31,838 --> 00:47:33,203
不是你的
It's not yours

570
00:47:37,644 --> 00:47:38,576
我走了！
I leave now!

571
00:47:47,121 --> 00:47:47,984
拜拜！
Goodbye!

572
00:47:58,299 --> 00:47:59,561
阿娥在吗？
Is Ah-ngor here?

573
00:47:59,733 --> 00:48:01,758
她不在，是谁找她呀？
She is not here. Who are you?

574
00:48:03,571 --> 00:48:05,596
不用了，谢谢！
It's alright. Thanks

575
00:49:40,468 --> 00:49:41,126
小姐！
Lady!

576
00:49:41,502 --> 00:49:42,399
什么事？
What's the matter?

577
00:49:42,602 --> 00:49:43,626
阿娥在吗？
Is Ah-ngor here?

578
00:49:43,837 --> 00:49:46,237
不清楚，她好像去了九龙还没回来
I'm not sure! She had went to Kowloon and still haven't returned

579
00:49:47,341 --> 00:49:47,704
去了九龙？！
To Kowloon?

580
00:49:47,741 --> 00:49:48,672
是呀！
Yes!

581
00:49:51,412 --> 00:49:52,139
谢谢！
Thank you

582
00:49:52,246 --> 00:49:53,177
不客气！
You're welcome

583
00:50:45,333 --> 00:50:46,459
几时来的？
When did you arrive?

584
00:50:48,336 --> 00:50:49,496
刚刚来的？
I just arrived

585
00:50:55,109 --> 00:50:56,474
你好像肥了些！
You look a bit fatter than before

586
00:50:59,679 --> 00:51:00,703
少少！
A little bit

587
00:51:01,549 --> 00:51:02,742
你也是！
So are you

588
00:51:04,185 --> 00:51:07,211
全靠他，他是我的医生
It's all because of him He's my doctor

589
00:51:13,194 --> 00:51:14,593
你今晚在这里过夜？！
Would you stay up here tonight?

590
00:51:15,829 --> 00:51:18,992
不…我现在要回去了
No... I'm going home now

591
00:51:27,741 --> 00:51:28,469
阿娥
Ah-ngor!

592
00:51:31,878 --> 00:51:36,110
我想告诉你，我找到那只杯啦！
I just wanted to you tell that I've found that glass

593
00:52:33,606 --> 00:52:34,573
张小姐CaII你
Miss Cheung called you just now

594
00:52:34,741 --> 00:52:36,038
她说她现在正赶去梅窝码头
She said that she was going to the pier of Silver-mine Bay

595
00:52:36,243 --> 00:52:37,766
叫你无论如何都要等她
and told you to wait for her anyway

596
00:54:42,802 --> 00:54:43,962
你可以先上去睡觉
You may go to sleep

597
00:54:44,138 --> 00:54:45,627
明天我再帮你Checkin
& I'll check in for you tomorrow

598
00:54:47,074 --> 00:54:47,971
好
OK!

599
00:55:07,261 --> 00:55:08,558
明早几点返工？
When do you go to work next morning?

600
00:55:08,962 --> 00:55:12,761
很早的，我煮早餐你吃好吗？
Very early! I'll make breakfast for you

601
00:55:13,933 --> 00:55:14,921
好
Good!

602
00:55:19,639 --> 00:55:21,231
你打算住多久？
How long will you live in here?

603
00:55:23,143 --> 00:55:24,269
无所谓
It depends!

604
00:55:41,595 --> 00:55:42,925
我先走了
I leave now

605
00:55:45,299 --> 00:55:46,425
我送你
I see you off

606
00:55:46,733 --> 00:55:48,700
不用了，很近呀
That's OK! It's near

607
00:55:50,970 --> 00:55:52,630
你今晚可以不回去吗？
Would you not go home tonight?

608
00:55:56,510 --> 00:55:58,033
为什么到现在才来找我？
Why do you not visit me until now?

609
00:56:02,615 --> 00:56:04,549
因为我自己知道自己的事
Because, I know myself clearly

610
00:56:06,086 --> 00:56:07,814
我不可以答应你些什么
I cannot promise you anything

611
00:56:11,191 --> 00:56:17,823
如果我不是挂着你，我不会进来找你
If I'm not missing you, I won't visit you today

612
00:56:20,367 --> 00:56:22,392
如果你再不来找我
If you don't visit me in these days

613
00:56:22,735 --> 00:56:24,566
我可能同那个医生结婚
I will probably marry that doctor

614
00:57:29,470 --> 00:57:32,700
鱼蛋佬，我要一元，要多点酱
Fish-ball guy, give me one dollar of fish-ball with more dressing

615
00:57:40,280 --> 00:57:44,512
摆呀，怎么不摆？多点酱嘛
Take it, why don't you take it? You've said you want more dressing!

616
00:57:44,884 --> 00:57:48,012
摆呀，不摆我会庆的
Take it or I'll get mad

617
00:57:51,791 --> 00:57:54,885
鱼蛋佬？！你妈的！
Fish-ball guy? Damn you!

618
00:57:56,497 --> 00:58:00,694
不是吧，乌蝇哥，怎么霉成这样？
It won't, Mr Fly! Why are you so poor?

619
00:58:00,900 --> 00:58:02,424
搞到摆鱼蛋档？！
You don't have to sell fish-ball, do you?

620
00:58:03,003 --> 00:58:06,029
阴功罗
Poor guy

621
00:58:06,939 --> 00:58:08,803
一定是你大佬指使你的
It must be your Big Brother who told you to do so

622
00:58:09,675 --> 00:58:11,802
你呀就不要跟他了
You should leave your Big Brother

623
00:58:11,911 --> 00:58:15,403
你看我的马，个个身光颈靓
Look at my followers, all dressed up!

624
00:58:15,549 --> 00:58:17,448
摆大哥电话，用得着做吗？
Taking wireless telephone, do you need that?

625
00:58:17,984 --> 00:58:20,111
你跟的那个大佬
You bastard! Your Big Brother sent you

626
00:58:20,287 --> 00:58:21,651
叫你站在街上卖鱼蛋
selling fish-ball in the street

627
00:58:21,854 --> 00:58:23,378
跟我不是更好
Working for me is better!

628
00:58:23,623 --> 00:58:24,920
走鬼呀！
Escape

629
00:58:29,129 --> 00:58:31,256
走什么走呢？你是古惑仔呀
Escape for what? You are a gangster!

630
00:58:31,398 --> 00:58:32,762
有这么多兄弟在这里，你怕差人？！
We have so crowd of gangsters here! It's no need to afraid!

631
00:58:32,932 --> 00:58:33,727
动他呀！
Beat him!

632
00:58:36,236 --> 00:58:38,931
不用怕，有什么事进去了也不用怕
Don't be afraid! You'll be alright even if you're in jail

633
00:58:39,073 --> 00:58:40,370
有人敢动你马上还手
Fight back at one if someone beat you

634
00:58:40,507 --> 00:58:41,599
不要影衰班兄弟
Don't make us lose faces

635
00:58:42,209 --> 00:58:43,835
你这衰人，你…
You bastard, you...

636
00:58:44,011 --> 00:58:46,241
不用这么紧张，没事的
Take it easy! It's OK!

637
00:58:46,380 --> 00:58:48,745
你又不是卖白粉，只是卖鱼蛋嘛
You are not selling drugs, just fish-ball

638
00:58:49,849 --> 00:58:50,610
看戏！
Something good to be seen

639
00:59:24,984 --> 00:59:25,881
打四万啦！
Beat him!

640
00:59:39,333 --> 00:59:41,823
他妈的，别走呀！
Hey, don't go you bastard

641
00:59:42,569 --> 00:59:43,796
还走？
Don't go!

642
00:59:45,405 --> 00:59:46,531
去死啦！
Go to hell, bastard!

643
01:00:02,422 --> 01:00:04,389
拖他过来！
Take him here

644
01:00:14,001 --> 01:00:15,298
饮完啦！
Finished drinking

645
01:00:18,172 --> 01:00:20,105
对了，两箱鸡翼你猜有多少只？
Right! How many chicken wings are there in two boxes

646
01:00:21,542 --> 01:00:23,133
二、三百只啦！
About two or three hundreds!

647
01:00:24,511 --> 01:00:26,137
二、三百只？！
Two or three hundreds?

648
01:00:31,151 --> 01:00:33,517
喂，你回去了记得告诉你老板
Hey, go back and tell your boss...

649
01:00:33,653 --> 01:00:37,885
以后不要再叫你一个人搬
not to send you to take thing

650
01:00:38,125 --> 01:00:39,422
这么重的东西
so heavy alone

651
01:00:39,560 --> 01:00:42,687
告诉他，一只鸡翼打一捶
Or else, I'll give him one fist for one wing in return

652
01:00:43,629 --> 01:00:44,561
神经病！
You are crazy

653
01:00:44,697 --> 01:00:45,685
我神经病？
I am crazy?

654
01:00:48,968 --> 01:00:50,696
是不是不想我帮你？
Do you want me to help you?

655
01:00:50,870 --> 01:00:53,361
无所谓，反正我都不打算做了
It's OK! Anyway, I will quit!

656
01:00:53,706 --> 01:00:58,302
不做，为什么？
Quit! Why?

657
01:00:59,946 --> 01:01:01,971
我想到九龙去找工做
I want to find a job in Kowloon

658
01:01:03,883 --> 01:01:06,511
好呀，方便我，搬到我家来呀
Good! It's doing me favour! You can live in my house!

659
01:01:08,355 --> 01:01:09,946
你不要讲第二次
Don't say the second time

660
01:01:10,723 --> 01:01:12,281
讲了第二次就收不回了
You can't deny it if you say it twice

661
01:01:14,027 --> 01:01:15,687
我不是讲笑的
I'm not kidding!

662
01:01:16,896 --> 01:01:18,658
我出了去就不会再回来
I go out and will never come back

663
01:01:30,210 --> 01:01:31,642
喂，你吃什么呀？
Hey, what do you want to eat?

664
01:01:40,853 --> 01:01:43,344
你告诉他，我会准时上竹馆找他
Tell him that I'll go to find him on time

665
01:01:43,856 --> 01:01:45,881
如果乌蝇少了一条毛，唯他是问
If Fly has anything wrong, he'll pay for it

666
01:01:46,126 --> 01:01:46,955
就这样啦
It's finished!

667
01:01:48,661 --> 01:01:49,685
什么事呀？
What's the matter?

668
01:01:50,330 --> 01:01:52,729
没什么，我现在要出去，乌蝇出了事
Nothing special! Fly has some problem and I'm going out now

669
01:01:52,932 --> 01:01:54,092
会不会有危险？！
Would it be dangerous?

670
01:01:54,301 --> 01:01:57,498
没事的，我今晚就回来放心
No, it'll be alright, I'll be back tonight

671
01:03:07,240 --> 01:03:09,173
土申叔，这么多人呀？
Uncle Kwan, so many people here?

672
01:03:09,343 --> 01:03:12,311
华仔，这件事是乌蝇不对
Ah-wah, it's Fly doing wrong in this case

673
01:03:12,512 --> 01:03:15,776
不过，大家是自己人，无谓搞大了
But, I don't want to make it big since we all know each other

674
01:03:16,249 --> 01:03:19,046
过去跟TOny讲几句好话吧！
Say something good to Tony & the case will be settled

675
01:03:29,196 --> 01:03:32,631
TOny，乌蝇就算有什么不对
Tony, no matter what did Fly do,

676
01:03:32,765 --> 01:03:34,198
我都会执行家法
I'll punish him according to my rules

677
01:03:34,867 --> 01:03:36,300
请你把我细佬交给我
So please give me back my brother

678
01:03:36,470 --> 01:03:39,870
细佬？！什么细佬呀？
Brother? What kind of brother?

679
01:03:40,040 --> 01:03:42,872
这个是细佬吗？你喜欢掩住你的细佬
Is this a brother? You like to protect your brother

680
01:03:43,043 --> 01:03:44,976
现在掩住他呀
now you are protecting him!

681
01:03:45,644 --> 01:03:49,444
同我玩花样？是好马就该掩住他
Making fun of me? You should protect him if he is good

682
01:03:49,615 --> 01:03:52,584
你掩住“劈”屎，你怎么做人大佬呀
Now you are just protecting a lump of shit How can you be a Big Brother?

683
01:03:52,752 --> 01:03:54,719
TOny，拿回个彩就算了
Tony, stop when you have some advantage

684
01:03:54,887 --> 01:03:55,716
无谓去得这么尽
Don't go too far

685
01:03:55,888 --> 01:03:59,289
坤叔，你省省吧，我是教识他做人
Uncle Kwan, save it for yourself! I'm teaching him to grow up

686
01:04:00,060 --> 01:04:02,255
他的马可以这样对我
His gangster can treat me like this

687
01:04:02,828 --> 01:04:04,795
将来你们还有地方立足吗？
Where can we stand in the future then?

688
01:04:05,599 --> 01:04:08,123
人呢，我一定会做
I'll release him surely!

689
01:04:08,368 --> 01:04:11,268
不过一定要我麻，我的要求好低
But I must be satisfied My requirement is low

690
01:04:11,438 --> 01:04:13,132
只要你讲一句我喜欢听的
Just say one sentence I like

691
01:04:13,340 --> 01:04:14,568
我就速速放人
I'll release him

692
01:04:20,380 --> 01:04:21,937
这句说话你喜不喜欢听？
Do you like to hear these words

693
01:04:21,981 --> 01:04:23,039
你要不要你弟弟？
Do you want your brother?

694
01:04:23,183 --> 01:04:24,046
华仔！
Ah-wah!

695
01:04:44,204 --> 01:04:45,727
大佬！
Big Brother

696
01:04:51,077 --> 01:04:52,271
你好！
Are you alright?

697
01:04:55,215 --> 01:04:56,273
能不能走？
Can you walk?

698
01:04:58,318 --> 01:04:59,512
能！
Yes, I can

699
01:05:09,563 --> 01:05:12,053
你的“靓”扶起他，叫呀！
Tell your follower to help him stand

700
01:05:12,532 --> 01:05:13,520
扶起他！
Help him stand

701
01:05:15,168 --> 01:05:18,501
不用，我自己起来！
No, I can stand by myself

702
01:05:47,833 --> 01:05:49,323
我自己走可以了
I can walk by myself

703
01:06:02,048 --> 01:06:03,106
不要过来
Don't get near to me

704
01:06:05,285 --> 01:06:06,148
大佬！大佬！
Big Brother! Big Brother!

705
01:06:15,694 --> 01:06:16,786
我告诉你们俩
I tell you two,

706
01:06:16,929 --> 01:06:18,896
这件事就算找天皇出来也没得拆
this case can't be settled even if you bring the highest King

707
01:06:32,145 --> 01:06:36,911
乌蝇，这件事情肯定还有下文
Fly, this case certainly won't end up this way

708
01:06:37,083 --> 01:06:38,071
这些钱你拿去
You take this money

709
01:06:38,385 --> 01:06:40,909
回调景岭要等事情淡了些才好出来
And go back to Til-gang Lin and wait for the case to fade out

710
01:06:41,087 --> 01:06:42,111
我不回去！
I won't go!

711
01:06:42,821 --> 01:06:43,412
我发过誓
I've made a vow

712
01:06:43,622 --> 01:06:45,920
我不发达就不回调景岭见我老妈
I won't go back to see my mother if I do not succeed

713
01:06:47,826 --> 01:06:50,920
好，我同你去大屿山
OK, I go to Lantau Island with you

714
01:06:52,465 --> 01:06:53,624
为什么你一定要我走呢？
Why do you drive me away so insistly?

715
01:06:53,766 --> 01:06:57,099
为什么？我不想明天你一出门口
Why? I don't want you to be killed tomorrow

716
01:06:57,337 --> 01:06:58,701
就被人斩开几碌
when you go out

717
01:06:59,838 --> 01:07:00,998
你明知道那只是癫狗
You know he is just a mad dog

718
01:07:01,174 --> 01:07:03,267
为什么你不听我的话，偏要去惹他
Why don't you listen to me not to provoke him?

719
01:07:03,476 --> 01:07:06,774
不是我惹他，是他先来惹我呀
It's him who provoked me, I didn't provoke him

720
01:07:06,946 --> 01:07:09,380
难道我不该玩他，现在我玩他不起吗
Don't you think I should just about it! I have the power to play, haven't I?

721
01:07:10,749 --> 01:07:12,148
你玩得起吗？！
Don't you have the power to play with him?

722
01:07:13,219 --> 01:07:16,153
你玩得起就不会被人打到像个猪头炳
If you have, you won't be beaten so heavily and have face swollen up

723
01:07:19,159 --> 01:07:21,956
是，我是被人打得像猪头炳
Yes, I was beaten to have face swollen

724
01:07:22,095 --> 01:07:24,359
你嫌我映衰你，就别理我好了
You are blaming me on losing you face, you can leave me alone

725
01:07:29,569 --> 01:07:34,562
是你自己说的，不要贪口爽呀
No one force you to speak this Don't speak it for fun

726
01:07:36,209 --> 01:07:37,869
我现在就不理你
I leave you alone now

727
01:07:38,144 --> 01:07:39,577
如果你明天出门口没事的话
If you are safe when you go out tomorrow

728
01:07:39,812 --> 01:07:41,143
我就替你挽鞋
I'll do anything for you

729
01:08:23,822 --> 01:08:26,086
我们一向都不知道明天会怎么样？
We all don't know what will happen tomorrow

730
01:08:26,992 --> 01:08:28,016
对不对？
Do you agree?

731
01:08:39,072 --> 01:08:39,901
去宵夜
Let's go eating out!

732
01:08:43,476 --> 01:08:44,407
走啦
Come along!

733
01:09:18,445 --> 01:09:19,274
打他
Beat him!

734
01:09:23,749 --> 01:09:26,240
乌蝇，我灭你，我灭死你呀！
Fly, I twist your face I twist you to death

735
01:09:29,189 --> 01:09:31,248
这次我还暗算不到你
I can plot against you this time, can't I?

736
01:09:32,492 --> 01:09:33,753
你不要打我大佬呀
