什么事呀？
What is going on?

923
01:29:59,451 --> 01:30:01,384
没有，我知你怕热
Nothing. I know you don't like feeling hot

924
01:30:01,619 --> 01:30:03,484
买了一部冷气给你
So I buy you a air conditioner

925
01:30:04,289 --> 01:30:07,621
我们下面装了，你留给自己用吧
We're installed it down there. This one just leave in to you

926
01:30:08,826 --> 01:30:11,556
我不上来了，你爸爸在
I don't come up. Your father is here

927
01:30:12,431 --> 01:30:14,796
那个是你老公，不是我爸爸
He's your husband, not my father

928
01:30:50,768 --> 01:30:52,395
你走到几时才安乐呀
When will you calm down and stop escaping?

929
01:30:53,271 --> 01:30:54,760
你出来找我做什么？
Why did you come out to see me?

930
01:30:55,940 --> 01:30:57,498
你不要理我好不好？
Why don't you leave me alone?

931
01:30:59,244 --> 01:31:02,475
我不理你？我不理你那个理你呀？
Who will care for you if I don't?

932
01:31:09,221 --> 01:31:11,688
不要以为做完这件事就好威了
Don't think that you'll be famous after this task

933
01:31:13,724 --> 01:31:19,458
对，你今天做完，个个就会说你够姜
Right, everybody will say you are brave this time when you do that

934
01:31:21,133 --> 01:31:23,294
下个礼拜，还有人知道你是那一个
But no one will remember you next week

935
01:31:24,536 --> 01:31:25,968
但是那又怎么样？
But what become of you then?

936
01:31:26,505 --> 01:31:28,631
再迟点就没有人认识你乌蝇啦
No one will know you later

937
01:31:41,053 --> 01:31:43,317
我也为阿公做了不少事
I've done many things for godfather also

938
01:31:46,058 --> 01:31:50,926
我十四岁，十四岁就拿安家费
I had received money for death when I was fourteen

939
01:31:54,199 --> 01:31:55,756
我威过好多人啦？
I was greater than a lot of people, right?

940
01:31:56,801 --> 01:31:59,735
那又怎么样？现在不也是这个样子
But look at me! I'm just an ordinary man now

941
01:32:00,072 --> 01:32:03,768
你威风，你总算威风过呀
Anyway, you were famous for sometime!

942
01:32:04,875 --> 01:32:08,106
我呢？我怎么样？
But what about me?

943
01:32:10,748 --> 01:32:13,979
没有人看得起我，你就开心啦
No one notice me and you are happy about that

944
01:32:14,486 --> 01:32:16,385
我样样都被人家看小
People look down upon everything of me

945
01:32:16,687 --> 01:32:19,485
他们还说我是你裤档里的一条狗
They even said that I was a dog beneath you ass

946
01:32:19,657 --> 01:32:20,954
你知不知道？
Do you know that?

947
01:32:24,695 --> 01:32:27,629
我乌蝇宁愿做一日英雄
I would rather be three-minute hero

948
01:32:27,832 --> 01:32:29,765
都不想做一世乌蝇
I don't want to be a fly for all my life

949
01:32:32,070 --> 01:32:34,765
你让我一手一脚的做一件事好不好？
Let me finish a great task on my own, would you?

950
01:32:35,440 --> 01:32:36,872
就这一次啦
Just for this time

951
01:32:51,456 --> 01:32:56,893
好，你是不是决定要去？
OK! Did you decide to go?

952
01:32:58,530 --> 01:33:00,292
如果你去我就陪你去
I'll go with you if you want to

953
01:33:01,466 --> 01:33:03,194
要是你被人射到了我都替你补飞
I'll take revenge for you if you are shoot down

954
01:33:03,368 --> 01:33:06,200
你不要对我这么好呀，行不行？
Don't treat me so good, would you?

955
01:33:10,342 --> 01:33:12,241
我还你不起的
I can't pay you back

956
01:33:13,844 --> 01:33:15,834
我不想跟你讲这么多话
I don't want to talk so much with you

957
01:33:15,980 --> 01:33:18,107
只要你说去，我就陪你去
Just say it, and I'll go with you

958
01:33:19,551 --> 01:33:23,543
如果你不去的话，一齐回大屿山
We'll go to Lantau Island if you say no

959
01:33:26,824 --> 01:33:28,791
以后的事，我会搞定
I'll settle anything following

960
01:33:36,000 --> 01:33:40,334
好！好！好！
OK! OK! OK!

961
01:33:40,539 --> 01:33:41,800
我跟你回去
I go back with you

962
01:33:57,688 --> 01:33:58,985
阿财，阿财，你不要看不起人
Ah-choi, Ah-choi

963
01:33:59,191 --> 01:34:00,680
怎么你残成这样？
Don't look down upon other

964
01:34:01,193 --> 01:34:03,559
快点同大佬打招呼了
He used to be great and famous but now he was finished

965
01:34:05,030 --> 01:34:08,591
不要这么独食，分一些给阿财啦
Don't be so stingily! Give something to Ah-cho

